Iv lived in minnesota for 4 months now. it seems like 20 years... or more. so much has happined. now i sit here typing wondering what tomorrow is gonna bring. thats the best thing about it. you never know what tomorrow will be like. it could be the best day of my life. and thats what keeps me going. hope. knowing someday something will go right. i just hope that someday comes soon.

dude... its been a while. iv died and came back to life. iv moved to minneota iv totaled me car iv worked contrution. iv gotten fired, iv been to the hospital im in debt. i claim bankruptcy i loose everything, i get head injury, i get memory lapses. really freaky. BUT IM STILL ALIVE!!! live sucks but oh well. i found the internet again... i miss my band i hate q tips and horses. i want to find a life i can live. i need a job. i need help. but i dont care. anyways. i miss alot of people i plan to visit washington someday. that would be sweet. im almost 20. ill peace out.. my # 218-849-0619 for all my old friends if they want to talk to me. have a great day. peace out

i can go on the net now and write cause im in wonderful colorado. My head has been twisted. Dont know what to think. Sunday afternoon i was going to work like usual. then the phone rings. its the phone call that killed. My Dad died. heart attack. not expected. i couldent bealive it. that night i was on my way to colorado. still couldent bealive it. got here and dad isnt around. thats when it all started to sink in. I miss him. even through all the troubles we had. i love him. hes my dad. hes made me who i am. and now hes gone. we went to the mortuary today. did all the hibituary stuff. got a coffen. thats when i realized that i would never see him anymore. talk to him anymore. i wish i could have said goodbye. i wish i could have told him that i love him. iv not been able to sleep that well. think that well. my mom isnt doing well. iv seen all my sibilings cry at least once already. i just cant bealive it. life wont be the same.

dad
you are in my heart 
i wish this world wouldent have torn us apart
siting here waiting for this moment to end
your smile is in every tear 
i miss you
i love you
rest in peace

i must say, this trip has sucked so bad so far! ok im going to recap from friday to now.  "tuesday night"

walking into my house after being out of it for over a year was crazy.. all kinda of studd i left behind.. my room was how i left it. I felt like this is where i was soppost to be this last year.. but i started thinking.. no no no washington is where i was soppost to be..

Friday
woke up sick... got sicker as the day went on
2 hours waiting at the airport and a fever starts up,
i watch tv on plane, i sware i was the only person on that plane. thats when my throat really kicked it up and hurt. when i get to denver my brothers picked me up. it was nice seing them...then BOOM the sickness hit me with a bang!
Saterday
sick in bed with fever up to 103.5
Sunday
sick in bed with fever up to 103
Monday
fever gone! ya! still sick, didnt have the strength to do anything. went to pick up my brother from spain. it was nice seeing him
Teusday
still got this headache and troat cough and now my nose is expelling stuff all day. ahh i just want to have fun here without bodily pain!
so far its been alright here otherwise.. i missed out on alot cause of the fever. it was crazy, i tryed to get some water once.. and i was sooo dizzy that i fell.. i probably looked drunk..

tomorrow i leave for kansas! aww yea

Hope you my homies are hving a great time back there.
peace
